@drchatterjee joined me on a past epsiode of The Doctor’s Farmacy where he explained how focusing on other things besides our diet, like sleeping a full eight hours can help tremendously in feeling better and making healthier decisions throughout the day. He also explained why personalization is key and much more.⁣
⁣
You can listen to the full episode, “The Secret To Losing Weight And Feeling Great”, on your favorite podcast app.⁣
